casebody.data:
BARRIE
v.
ROSENBLUM S065980 Supreme Court of Oregon. June 12, 2018

Petitioner's arguments that the Attorney General's certified ballot title for Initiative Petition No. 40 (2018) does not comply substantially with ORS 250.035(2) are not well taken. The court certifies to the Secretary of State the Attorney General's certified ballot title for the proposed ballot measure.
